OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has ruled out more help 
OL,6, for homes with energy bills despite    
OL,7, costs remaining historically high.     
OL,9,FOn Thursday, Ofgem is expected to      
OL,10,Fannounce a sharp drop in the price cap,
OL,11,Fwhich limits how much suppliers can    
OL,12,Fcharge per unit of energy.             
OL,14,FIt is forecast to fall to about #2,000,
OL,15,Fnearly double the amount when the cap  
OL,16,Fwas announced in 2019.                 
OL,18,FEnvironment Secretary Therese Coffey   
OL,19,Fsaid the chancellor had already set out
OL,20,Fhis plan to help homes months ago.     
